係聖靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三為一體係有，當中包括聖父，聖子（升天後既耶穌），聖靈，聖靈保惠師係聖經上有出現過，聖靈使人說方言</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以求教三為一體係邊章邊節出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb29a59babc40407584ff271bd1c0970c23f6d5a","tid":495003,"uid":148251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"聽聞神係全能全知，咁神可唔可以創造一舊佢舉唔起嘅石頭或者創作一條佢唔知答案嘅問題。"},{"pid":"3a3bd4a7f3419ee8068b7618a7240bc62de3c7b6","tid":495003,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽聞神係全能全知，咁神可唔可以創造一舊佢舉唔起嘅石頭或者創作一條佢唔知答案嘅問題。</blockquote><br />\n聖經話神唔會做呢啲嘢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3127da6f42231e5554d4259cfc499858f38a9898","tid":495003,"uid":148251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽聞神係全能全知，咁神可唔可以創造一舊佢舉唔起嘅石頭或者創作一條佢唔知答案嘅問題。</blockquote><br />\n聖經話神唔會做呢啲嘢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢仲係唔係全能全知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d667ae4d477f985ff9be74aa93a3f46aa5612e","tid":495003,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽聞神係全能全知，咁神可唔可以創造一舊佢舉唔起嘅石頭或者創作一條佢唔知答案嘅問題。</blockquote><br />\n聖經話神唔會做呢啲嘢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢仲係唔係全能全知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依條咁既問題係 神比我地既考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n異端<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42e2710945ea56c480ad74f